{"tid":1566342,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］美兩眾議員奶共 反對民主人權法案","createTime":"2019-09-13T13:56:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T06:52:36.000Z","uid":90012,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"26056f25e7e35134bacd832c4975211ea651ab1b","tid":1566342,"uid":90012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T13:56:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=741125973003507&amp;id=347501365699305\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D741125973003507%26id%3D347501365699305&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88hZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=abe5002e\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=741125973003507&amp;id=347501365699305</a><br />\n<br />\n香港狀況危急<br />\n<br />\n美國兩位眾議員或與中共和談。親中的民主黨員 Rick Larsen 更表明反對通過《香港人權及民主法案》，認為香港政府聽取民意就足夠。另一位，是共和黨的 Darin Lahood。<br />\n<br />\n不要以為中共不會用黑金美給美國國會議員。香港這次輸掉，我們會被滅族的。新疆維吾爾族怎樣，香港也可以。現在是危急之時，不是戰勝之時 。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以在推文中清楚表達香港人的意願。<br />\n<br />\n兩位眾議員的標文：<br />\n@replahood<br />\n@RepRickLarsen<br />\n<br />\n相關 Twitter 推文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/usip/status/1171786710063157249?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fusip%2Fstatus%2F1171786710063157249%3Fs%3D21&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88hZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=8e838933\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fusip%2Fstatus%2F1171786710063157249%3Fs%3D21&h=64e49f77\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/usip/status/1171786710063157249?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全部人上Twitter做野，但係請保持禮貌</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EExDwmS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEExDwmS.jpg&h=16c19eac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be6fa0cbaa38f836e770ae78e41b05c5bdbcd15c","tid":1566342,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T13:57:00.000Z","msg":"[國際戰線] 香港人唔可以當其他國家係Condom!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1565130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1565130</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/thrHTWT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FthrHTWT.jpg&h=21d791c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"edab5bd69fe01c189ddb5a26dadb059871ce2963","tid":1566342,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T13:57:25.000Z","msg":"[國際戰線] 香港人唔可以當其他國家係Condom!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1565130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1565130</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/thrHTWT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FthrHTWT.jpg&h=21d791c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ddccd0fab1bafac6454b4ce2dba6d9345e718e18","tid":1566342,"uid":101537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T13:59:04.000Z","msg":"共和黨支持㗎嘛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TT5NoYN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTT5NoYN.jpg&h=6894a64b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GvUKrb8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGvUKrb8.jpg&h=ec6b4d48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">12點英領和平請願<br />\n灰磚範圍 英國領土</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2點打後 銅鑼灣自由活動!</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【國際戰線】又係我，前英領職員，915見（2）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1565523\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1565523</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cc28e494cb3cbd49f80ffbb7a2cefd279d21ce1c","tid":1566342,"uid":90012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T14:03:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e4cf5ff78791b26374b17812c11517a02432f20","tid":1566342,"uid":90012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T14:03:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab6eb734831159f7be7462f8c49e031fee86ac63","tid":1566342,"uid":197492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T14:03:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"af99e66d663f0ff06aee45b563c7094a318585ae","tid":1566342,"uid":90012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T14:04:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31831e825239293c6cd4d43f95a461be6ef8bace","tid":1566342,"uid":245841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T14:05:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"37cfdb209fddc44b2cacc8fab7e308f47ea51a24","tid":1566342,"uid":262618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T14:07:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ab294d9482a29aef5c301fadd49543dbdc5e983","tid":1566342,"uid":90012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T14:08:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"be275b9621a6e6e6be1e6f4a3a76aee7f84a9dfd","tid":1566342,"uid":98317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T14:10:59.000Z","msg":"PUsh"},{"pid":"300f4078027f8d04b9f03e6e5da6ffdc7e177ab9","tid":1566342,"uid":283494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T14:11:42.000Z","msg":"唔好以為美國奉旨支持你。<br />\n<br />\n要美國支持香港? 美國有咩著數先? 退一步諗,美國唔支持香港, 美國會唔會好大鑊?<br />\n<br />\n今日林鄭見在港央企, 等於宣佈香港經濟日後會由央企話事,損害所有外資企業在港利益。何不好好利用呢個核彈?<br />\n<br />\n另外,美國支持香港人,可以利用香港作為牽制中國的棋子,香港人又可利用美國保持生活自由, 雙方互利。"},{"pid":"8e407c41bc6c4492526554b6ca053a84d8fc4aea","tid":1566342,"uid":306816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply